    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">Added a few other things by request; now you can just send the current line with :CPosttoTwitter, and also I hacked together the ability to post visually selected text. To send visualized text; visual select the text and press T, thats a capital t. All the functionality to send visualized text is through a map that will yank the text, open a new tab, paste the text run the normal command :PosttoTwitter and then close the tab.</td>
